---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import ServicePage from '../templates/service/ServicePage.astro'
import ServiceSection from '../templates/service/ServiceSection.astro'
---

<ServicePage title="Senior Support Services">
  <Fragment slot="hero-image">
    <Image
      src={import('../assets/images/hero-image-1.png')}
      alt="A senior lady smiling and talking with her companion."
      loading="eager"
    />
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="heading">
    <span class="font-italic font-normal">Senior Support Services</span> in Bradford
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="hero-content">
    Missing appointments because driving doesn't feel safe anymore? Finding
    phone calls or shopping trips overwhelming? You're not alone - and you don't
    have to manage it all by yourself. Whether you're looking for support
    yourself or worried about a loved one, my elderly support services remove
    these frustrations with patient, one-to-one assistance—whether it's a
    hospital visit, grocery run, or managing appointments.
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="services">
    <ServiceSection
      id="transportation-to-appointments"
      number="01"
      heading="Transportation to Appointments"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Never let mobility challenges keep you from important visits. My
        reliable transport service for seniors ensures you get to
        <span class="font-semibold">medical appointments</span>,
        <span class="font-semibold">social outings</span>, and
        <span class="font-semibold">family visits</span> safely and on time. Whether
        it's a hospital check-up, or a trip to the hairdresser, I provide door-to-door
        assistance with walking aids and a patient, unhurried approach. Punctuality
        matters—so you'll never feel rushed or left waiting.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/light-domestic-cleaning-services.jpg')}
          alt="Light domestic cleaning services"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>

    <ServiceSection
      id="personal-shopping-assistance"
      number="02"
      heading="Personal Shopping Assistance"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        My personal shopping service for seniors takes the stress out of
        <span class="font-semibold"
          >buying clothes, gifts, and household essentials</span
        >. Whether you're looking for comfortable new slippers, a birthday
        present for a grandchild, or fresh bedding for your home, I'll help you
        choose exactly what you need.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/laundry-and-ironing-help.jpg')}
          alt="laundry and ironing help"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>

    <ServiceSection
      id="telephone-appointment-support"
      number="03"
      heading="Telephone Appointment Support"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        My telephone assistance service for seniors takes the stress out of
        <span class="font-semibold">managing appointments</span> and <span
          class="font-semibold">essential calls</span
        >. Whether you need to <span class="font-semibold">book a GP visit</span
        >, <span class="font-semibold">arrange a repair</span>, or <span
          class="font-semibold">understand medical letters</span
        >, I'll handle the calls for you—clearly, patiently, and without the
        frustration. No more missed appointments or unanswered questions—just
        reliable support to keep everything on track.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/personalised-meal-preparation.jpg')}
          alt="Personalised meal preparation"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>
  </Fragment>
</ServicePage>
